<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>File Download</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1037/1037316.png" type="image/png">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header img {
            height: 40px;
        }

        .header nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .header nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #000;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .header nav a:hover {
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .main-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .file-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .file-list li {
            background-color: white;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .file-list li:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0px 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .file-list a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .file-list .download-button {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .file-list .download-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .file-list .file-name {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .file-list .file-date {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .main-container h1 {
                font-size: 20px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .file-list li {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            .file-list .download-button {
                margin-top: 10px;
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <a href="/upload">
            <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1037/1037316.png" alt="FileTransfer Logo">
          </a>
       
    </header>

    <div class="main-container">
        <h1>Danh sách file bạn có thể tải xuống</h1>
        <p>Chọn file để tải xuống từ danh sách dưới đây.</p>

        <ul class="file-list">
            <% if (files.length > 0) { %>
                <% files.forEach(function(file) { %>
                    <li>
                        <div>
                            <div class="file-name"><%= file.name %></div>
                            <div class="file-date">Uploaded: <%= new Date(file.created_at).toLocaleString() %></div>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/files/download/<%= file.id %>" class="download-button" onclick="showDownloadAlert('<%= file.name %>')">Tải xuống</a>
                    </li>
                <% }); %>
            <% } else { %>
                <li>Không có file nào để tải xuống.</li>
            <% } %>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <script>
        function showDownloadAlert(fileName) {
            alert(`Bạn đang tải xuống file: ${fileName}`);
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
